             was indicted for <rs id="t18221204-71-off383" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18221204-71-off383" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18221204-71-off383" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               that he, on the <rs id="t18221204-71-cd384" type="crimeDate">17th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18221204-71-off383 t18221204-71-cd384"></join>, at St. Mary-le-bow, feloniously did utter and publish as true, a certain false, forged, and counterfeited deed
            </rs>, the tenor of which is as follows: -</p>
               <p>Setting forth the usual form of a power of Attorney, made in the joint names of 
               <persName id="t18221204-71-person617">
